  "title": "$1250 / 1br - 700ft² - Apartment furnished: 3 /12 all incl., fireplace in trendy neighbourhoo (Montreal) (map)",
  "body": "\nA Fireplace is available in one of the two apartments.<br />\n\t1 Bedroom, 1 Bathroom<br />\n\t700 square feet, 68 square meters<br />\n\tSleeps up to 4 people.<br />\n\tA practical work area.<br />\n\tHigh speed internet, sound system, television and cable<br />\n\tFurnished and all equipped.<br />\n<br />\nThese charming apartments are on the third floor of a completely renovated triplex. Everything is included in this bright and pleasant apartment.  The wood fireplace in the living room or one of the apartments provides a pleasant atmosphere during winter evenings.  One of the two balconies has a small table and two chairs to allow you to enjoy the sun at all hours of the day.<br />\n<br />\nThis is an ideal holidays or business accommodation for stays from one week to several months.  <br />\nThe apartment is situated in a quite and practical area. There is free street level parking. There are three Metro (subway) stations within 8 minutes walk away giving you easy and care free access to Montreal's activities, sites of interest and the different universities -McGill, UQAM and Montreal-.<br />\nA wonderful green space, Jarry Park, is within a few blocks.  Several swimming pools can be found there as well as tennis courts and a multitude of activities.  For your daily food shopping needs, for restaurants and a pleasant street life, the Jean-Talon Market is within 8 minutes walk.  This very popular open air market is renowned for its friendliness and European flavour.  Cafes and restaurants abound around the market as well as throughout the neighbourhood.<br />\n<br />\nIncluded:<br />\nAir conditioning, telephone, internet, cable TV, DVD, stereo, microwave, cookware &amp; utensils, washer-dryer, iron and ironing board and linen. <br />\nThe double sofa-bed can sleep two more people.  A spare single bed is available to accommodate yet another person.<br />\nAvailability:\t<br />\nSeptember 2012 (third floor)<br />\nNovember 2012 (second floor)<br />\nRates:   $1250 CDN / month<br />\n<br />\nContact:\tFrancine or Rhéal<br />\nResidence:\t514-750-5437<br />\nCellular:\t        514-591-2422<br />\nPlease indicate desired arrival date, length of stay and number of people. <br />\n\n<br /><br />\n\n<!-- START CLTAGS -->\n<br />\n\n\t\t\t<!-- CLTAG xstreet0=Henri-Julien -->\n\t\t\t<!-- CLTAG xstreet1=Villeray -->\n\t\t\t<!-- CLTAG city=Montreal -->\n\t\t\t<!-- CLTAG region=Qc -->\n\t\t\tHenri-Julien at Villeray\n\t\t\t<small>\n\t\t\t\t(<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://maps.google.com/?q=loc%3A+Henri%2DJulien+at+Villeray+Montreal+Qc+CA\">google map</a>)\n\t\t\t\t(<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://maps.yahoo.com/maps_result?addr=Henri%2DJulien+at+Villeray&amp;csz=Montreal+Qc&amp;country=CA\">yahoo map</a>)\n\t\t\t</small>\n\t\t<ul class=\"blurbs\">\n<li> <!-- CLTAG GeographicArea=Montreal -->Location: Montreal</li>\n<li>it's NOT ok to contact this poster with services or other commercial interests</li></ul>\n<!-- END CLTAGS -->\n",
